---
// Contact (§6): one artist, one inbox.
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Contact · GoteFigure" description="Get in touch with GoteFigure: orders, art, collabs.">
  <section class="info">
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p>
      GoteFigure is one person. Orders, sizing panic, collab ideas, or just to say the rabbit
      is creeping you out. It all goes to the same place:
    </p>
    <p class="email"><a href="mailto:hello@gotefigure.com" class="squiggle">hello@gotefigure.com</a></p>
    <p>
      Faster replies in the comments over on
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@gotefigure" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="squiggle">YouTube</a>.
      there’s a new drawing there most days.
    </p>
    <p class="margin-note">real responses, usually within a day or two</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .info { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--s-12) var(--s-6) var(--s-24); }
  .info h1 { margin-bottom: var(--s-6); }
  .info p { margin-bottom: var(--s-3); }
  .email { font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; }
</style>
